summary: A small mod to achieve a small purpose on stats.
descriptionHtml:
I don\'t know if a mod of this purpose is around.

This mod allows you to change your stat or someone else\'s stat from anyone. 
This mod might conflict mods that uses the small Jeremy since he\'s used as the middleman :D
You/someone will get his stats by default.
At current stage you will get/set all the stats from someone at a go.

spell\'s console code: XX000D66
The spell description has a bit more to say.

My Other mods:
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/30407]Body type change spell[/url]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/23028]Reviving followers[/url]
